<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>ArchiveBox Plugin Marketplace | abx-plugins</title>
    <meta
      name="description"
      content="Browse the ArchiveBox plugin ecosystem, including abx-plugins hooks, config options, source links, and example commands for ArchiveBox, abx-dl, and related web archiving tools."
    >
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Source+Serif+4:ital,opsz,wght@0,8..60,300;0,8..60,400;0,8..60,500;0,8..60,600;1,8..60,400&family=Inter+Tight:wght@400;500;600;700&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    >
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/tokens.css?v=1">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/base.css?v=1">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/components.css?v=1">
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: var(--ab-font-sans);
      }

      .hero {
        padding: var(--ab-s-8) 0 var(--ab-s-7);
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--ab-rule-strong);
      }

      .hero__masthead {
        display: block;
      }

      .hero__title {
        font-size: clamp(54px, 8vw, 96px);
        line-height: 0.92;
        letter-spacing: -0.04em;
        font-weight: 400;
        margin: 0;
        max-width: 10ch;
      }

      .hero__title em {
        color: var(--ab-accent);
        font-style: italic;
      }

      .hero__copy {
        margin-top: var(--ab-s-4);
        max-width: 56ch;
        font-family: var(--ab-font-serif);
        font-size: var(--ab-size-lg);
      }

      .hero__actions {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: var(--ab-s-3);
        margin-top: var(--ab-s-5);
      }

      .hero__stats {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 240px);
        gap: var(--ab-s-3);
        margin-top: var(--ab-s-6);
      }

      .stat {
        border: 1px solid var(--ab-rule-strong);
        background: var(--ab-bg-elev);
        padding: var(--ab-s-4);
        min-height: 104px;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        justify-content: space-between;
      }

      .stat strong {
        display: block;
        font-family: var(--ab-font-serif);
        font-size: clamp(30px, 3vw, 44px);
        line-height: 1;
        letter-spacing: -0.03em;
        color: var(--ab-fg);
      }

      .stat span {
        font-family: var(--ab-font-label);
        font-size: var(--ab-size-xs);
        letter-spacing: 0.18em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: var(--ab-fg-muted);
      }

      .hero__support {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: 6px;
        margin-top: var(--ab-s-4);
      }

      .hero__support code {
        font-size: 11px;
        padding: 4px 8px;
        background: var(--ab-bg-sunken);
        border: 1px solid var(--ab-rule);
        border-radius: var(--ab-r-1);
      }

      .hero-example {
        margin-top: var(--ab-s-7);
        border: 1px solid var(--ab-rule-strong);
        background: var(--ab-bg-elev);
      }

      .hero-example-header {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: flex-start;
        gap: var(--ab-s-4);
        padding: var(--ab-s-4) var(--ab-s-5);
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--ab-rule);
        background: var(--ab-bg-sunken);
      }

      .hero-example-title {
        margin: 0;
        font-family: var(--ab-font-label);
        font-size: var(--ab-size-xs);
        letter-spacing: 0.18em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: var(--ab-accent);
      }

      .hero-example-copy {
        margin: 6px 0 0;
        max-width: 54ch;
      }

      .hero-runner-links {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: var(--ab-s-2);
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        font-family: var(--ab-font-mono);
        font-size: var(--ab-size-xs);
        color: var(--ab-fg-muted);
      }

      .runner-link {
        text-decoration: none;
      }

      .hero-code-block {
        padding: var(--ab-s-4) var(--ab-s-5) var(--ab-s-5);
      }

      .hero-code-toolbar {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: center;
        gap: var(--ab-s-3);
        margin-bottom: var(--ab-s-3);
      }

      .hero-code-meta {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: var(--ab-s-2);
        align-items: center;
      }

      .hero-code-kicker {
        font-family: var(--ab-font-label);
        font-size: var(--ab-size-xs);
        letter-spacing: 0.16em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: var(--ab-fg-muted);
      }

      .copy-button,
      .run-tab {
        appearance: none;
        border: 1px solid var(--ab-rule-strong);
        background: var(--ab-bg-elev);
        color: var(--ab-fg);
        font-family: var(--ab-font-label);
        font-size: var(--ab-size-xs);
        letter-spacing: 0.08em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        padding: 8px 12px;
        cursor: pointer;
      }

      .copy-button:hover,
      .run-tab:hover {
        background: var(--ab-bg-sunken);
      }

      .hero-code-block .ab-terminal {
        box-shadow: none;
      }

      .hero-code-block .ab-terminal__body pre {
        font-size: var(--ab-size-sm);
        line-height: 1.7;
      }

      .install-details {
        padding: 0 var(--ab-s-5) var(--ab-s-5);
      }

      .install-details summary {
        cursor: pointer;
        font-family: var(--ab-font-label);
        font-size: var(--ab-size-xs);
        letter-spacing: 0.14em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: var(--ab-fg-muted);
      }

      .install-details pre {
        margin-top: var(--ab-s-3);
      }

      .install-details .ab-terminal {
        margin-top: var(--ab-s-3);
        box-shadow: none;
      }

      .catalog-toolbar {
        padding: var(--ab-s-5) 0;
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--ab-rule);
        position: sticky;
        top: 57px;
        z-index: 10;
        background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--ab-bg) 92%, transparent);
        backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      }

      .catalog-toolbar .ab-container,
      .catalog .ab-container {
        max-width: none;
      }

      .catalog-toolbar__grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr) auto;
        gap: var(--ab-s-3);
        align-items: end;
      }

      .searchbox {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 6px;
      }

      .searchbox__control {
        position: relative;
      }

      .searchbox__control input {
        padding-left: 38px;
        font-family: var(--ab-font-mono);
      }

      .searchbox__control svg {
        position: absolute;
        left: 12px;
        top: 50%;
        transform: translateY(-50%);
        color: var(--ab-fg-faint);
      }

      .result-count {
        font-family: var(--ab-font-mono);
        font-size: var(--ab-size-xs);
        color: var(--ab-fg-muted);
        white-space: nowrap;
        padding-bottom: 8px;
      }

      .catalog {
        padding: var(--ab-s-7) 0;
      }

      .catalog__head {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: end;
        gap: var(--ab-s-4);
        margin-bottom: var(--ab-s-5);
      }

      .catalog__head h2 {
        margin: 0;
      }

      .gallery {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(320px, 1fr));
        gap: var(--ab-s-4);
      }

      .plugin-card {
        border: 1px solid var(--ab-rule-strong);
        background: var(--ab-bg-elev);
        box-shadow: var(--ab-shadow-1);
      }

      .plugin-card summary {
        list-style: none;
        cursor: pointer;
      }

      .plugin-card summary::-webkit-details-marker {
        display: none;
      }

      .plugin-card summary:hover .plugin-card__frame,
      .plugin-card.modal-active .plugin-card__frame {
        border-color: var(--ab-accent);
        box-shadow: var(--ab-shadow-2);
      }

      .plugin-card__frame {
        display: block;
        padding: var(--ab-s-5);
        border: 1px solid transparent;
        transition: border-color var(--ab-dur-2) var(--ab-ease), box-shadow var(--ab-dur-2) var(--ab-ease);
      }

      .plugin-main h2 {
        margin: 0;
        font-size: var(--ab-size-xl);
      }

      .plugin-title-row {
        display: flex;
        align-items: baseline;
        gap: var(--ab-s-3);
        flex-wrap: wrap;
      }

      .plugin-slug {
        margin-top: 6px;
        color: var(--ab-fg-muted);
      }

      .plugin-summary-description {
        margin: var(--ab-s-3) 0 0;
      }

      .plugin-subline,
      .plugin-summary-facts,
      .hook-card-chips,
      .pill-list {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: 6px;
      }

      .plugin-subline {
        margin-top: var(--ab-s-4);
      }

      .plugin-summary-facts {
        margin-top: var(--ab-s-4);
      }

      .plugin-icon {
        width: 72px;
        height: 72px;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        border: 1px solid var(--ab-rule-strong);
        background: var(--ab-bg-sunken);
        color: var(--ab-accent);
        padding: 10px;
      }

      .plugin-icon svg,
      .plugin-icon .abx-output-icon,
      .plugin-icon .abx-output-icon svg {
        display: block;
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
      }

      .plugin-order {
        font-family: var(--ab-font-mono);
        font-size: var(--ab-size-xs);
        color: var(--ab-fg-faint);
      }

      .plugin-language {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        width: 22px;
        height: 22px;
        border: 1px solid var(--ab-rule);
        background: var(--ab-bg-sunken);
        color: var(--ab-fg-muted);
      }

      .chip {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 6px;
        min-height: 22px;
        padding: 3px 9px;
        border: 1px solid var(--ab-rule);
        background: var(--ab-bg-sunken);
        font-family: var(--ab-font-mono);
        font-size: 10px;
        color: var(--ab-ink-2);
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.06em;
      }

      .chip small {
        font-size: inherit;
        color: var(--ab-fg-muted);
      }

      .chip--link {
        text-decoration: none;
      }

      .chip--mime-html,
      .chip--mime-text,
      .chip--mime-doc {
        background: var(--ab-accent-wash);
      }

      .chip--mime-media {
        background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--ab-ochre) 14%, var(--ab-bg-elev));
      }

      .chip--mime-data,
      .chip--mime-code,
      .chip--mime-archive,
      .chip--mime-binary {
        background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--ab-slate) 12%, var(--ab-bg-elev));
      }

      .chip--bg-daemon {
        border-color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--ab-ochre) 32%, transparent);
        color: var(--ab-ochre);
      }

      .chip--bg-finite {
        border-color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--ab-moss) 32%, transparent);
        color: var(--ab-moss);
      }

      .chip--fg {
        border-color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--ab-slate) 32%, transparent);
        color: var(--ab-slate);
      }

      .plugin-body {
        padding: var(--ab-s-5);
      }

      .plugin-body > * + * {
        margin-top: var(--ab-s-5);
      }

      .plugin-modal-description {
        margin: 0;
        font-size: var(--ab-size-md);
      }

      .actions {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: var(--ab-s-3);
      }

      .section-title {
        margin: 0;
        padding-top: var(--ab-s-3);
        border-top: 1px solid var(--ab-rule);
      }

      .plugin-info-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
        gap: var(--ab-s-4);
      }

      .plugin-info-card {
        border: 1px solid var(--ab-rule);
        background: var(--ab-bg-sunken);
        padding: var(--ab-s-4);
      }

      .plugin-info-card > span:first-child,
      .hook-card-file,
      .footer-card-subtitle {
        display: block;
        margin-bottom: var(--ab-s-3);
        font-family: var(--ab-font-label);
        font-size: var(--ab-size-xs);
        letter-spacing: 0.16em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: var(--ab-fg-muted);
      }

      .run-tabs {
        border: 1px solid var(--ab-rule-strong);
      }

      .run-tabs-bar {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: 0;
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--ab-rule);
        background: var(--ab-bg-sunken);
      }

      .run-tab {
        border-width: 0 1px 0 0;
        background: transparent;
      }

      .run-tab.active {
        background: var(--ab-bg-elev);
        color: var(--ab-accent);
      }

      .run-tab-panel {
        display: none;
        border: 0;
        margin: 0;
        padding: var(--ab-s-4);
        background: #17130f;
        color: #ece4d0;
        overflow-x: auto;
        font-family: var(--ab-font-mono);
        font-size: var(--ab-size-sm);
        line-height: 1.7;
      }

      .run-tab-panel.active {
        display: block;
      }

      .note {
        margin: 0;
        font-style: italic;
        color: var(--ab-fg-muted);
      }

      .hook-list {
        display: grid;
        gap: var(--ab-s-3);
      }

      .hook-card {
        border: 1px solid var(--ab-rule);
        background: var(--ab-bg-sunken);
        padding: var(--ab-s-4);
      }

      .hook-card-phase {
        margin-left: auto;
        font-family: var(--ab-font-label);
        font-size: var(--ab-size-xs);
        letter-spacing: 0.12em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: var(--ab-accent);
      }

      .config-table-wrap {
        overflow-x: auto;
        border: 1px solid var(--ab-rule);
      }

      .config-table,
      .field-table,
      .env-table {
        width: 100%;
      }

      .config-key-desc {
        display: block;
        margin-top: 6px;
        font-size: var(--ab-size-sm);
        color: var(--ab-fg-muted);
      }

      .cfg-default {
        font-family: var(--ab-font-mono);
        font-size: var(--ab-size-xs);
      }

      .cfg-array,
      .cfg-obj {
        display: grid;
        gap: 4px;
        margin: 4px 0 4px 12px;
      }

      .cfg-obj-key,
      .cfg-bracket {
        color: var(--ab-fg-muted);
      }

      .cfg-string {
        color: var(--ab-accent);
      }

      .cfg-number {
        color: var(--ab-slate);
      }

      .cfg-bool-true {
        color: var(--ab-moss);
      }

      .cfg-bool-false,
      .cfg-null {
        color: var(--ab-ochre);
      }

      .config-table-muted {
        color: var(--ab-fg-faint);
      }

      .empty-state {
        padding: var(--ab-s-6);
        text-align: center;
        border: 1px dashed var(--ab-rule-strong);
        color: var(--ab-fg-muted);
        background: var(--ab-bg-elev);
      }

      .page-footer {
        padding: var(--ab-s-8) 0 var(--ab-s-7);
        border-top: 1px solid var(--ab-rule-strong);
        background: var(--ab-bg-sunken);
      }

      .footer-intro {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.15fr) minmax(0, 1fr);
        gap: var(--ab-s-6);
        align-items: start;
        margin-bottom: var(--ab-s-6);
      }

      .footer-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
        gap: var(--ab-s-4);
      }

      .footer-card {
        border: 1px solid var(--ab-rule);
        background: var(--ab-bg-elev);
        padding: var(--ab-s-5);
      }

      .footer-link-list {
        display: grid;
        gap: var(--ab-s-2);
      }

      .footer-link-item {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 28px minmax(0, 1fr);
        gap: var(--ab-s-3);
        padding: var(--ab-s-3) 0;
        border-top: 1px dashed var(--ab-rule);
        text-decoration: none;
      }

      .footer-link-item:first-child {
        border-top: 0;
        padding-top: 0;
      }

      .footer-link-copy strong {
        display: block;
        color: var(--ab-fg);
      }

      .footer-link-copy span {
        display: block;
        margin-top: 4px;
        color: var(--ab-fg-muted);
        font-size: var(--ab-size-sm);
      }

      .footer-meta {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        gap: var(--ab-s-3);
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        margin-top: var(--ab-s-6);
        padding-top: var(--ab-s-4);
        border-top: 1px solid var(--ab-rule);
        font-family: var(--ab-font-mono);
        font-size: var(--ab-size-xs);
        color: var(--ab-fg-muted);
      }

      .plugin-modal {
        width: min(1040px, calc(100vw - 40px));
        max-height: calc(100vh - 40px);
        padding: 0;
        border: 1px solid var(--ab-rule-strong);
        background: var(--ab-bg);
        color: var(--ab-fg);
        box-shadow: var(--ab-shadow-2);
      }

      .plugin-modal::backdrop {
        background: rgba(28, 24, 20, 0.45);
        backdrop-filter: blur(3px);
      }

      .plugin-modal-header {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        gap: var(--ab-s-4);
        align-items: center;
        padding: var(--ab-s-4) var(--ab-s-5);
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--ab-rule);
        background: var(--ab-bg-elev);
        position: sticky;
        top: 0;
        z-index: 1;
      }

      .plugin-modal-header-left {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 0;
        min-width: 0;
      }

      .plugin-modal-header-left h2 {
        margin: 0;
      }

      .plugin-modal-close {
        appearance: none;
        border: 1px solid var(--ab-rule-strong);
        background: var(--ab-bg);
        width: 34px;
        height: 34px;
        font-size: 22px;
        line-height: 1;
        cursor: pointer;
      }

      .plugin-modal-close:hover {
        background: var(--ab-bg-sunken);
      }

      .plugin-modal .plugin-body {
        max-height: calc(100vh - 120px);
        overflow-y: auto;
      }

      .ab-terminal code,
      .run-tab-panel code {
        background: none;
        border: 0;
        padding: 0;
        color: inherit;
      }

      .code-comment {
        color: #8f8675;
      }

      .code-command {
        color: #f0e4cd;
      }

      .code-option {
        color: #d6a654;
      }

      .code-string {
        color: #c26a6a;
      }

      .code-env {
        color: #8aa062;
      }

      .code-boolean {
        color: #d6a654;
      }

      .code-value {
        color: #c8bea8;
      }

      @media (max-width: 1100px) {
        .footer-intro,
        .plugin-info-grid {
          grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }

        .gallery {
          grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }
      }

      @media (max-width: 820px) {
        .ab-topbar {
          flex-wrap: wrap;
          justify-content: center;
        }

        .ab-topbar__nav {
          margin-left: 0;
          width: 100%;
          justify-content: center;
          flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .footer-grid {
          grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }

        .catalog-toolbar {
          position: static;
        }

        .catalog-toolbar__grid,
        .hero-example-header,
        .hero-code-toolbar,
        .plugin-card__frame {
          grid-template-columns: 1fr;
          flex-direction: column;
          align-items: flex-start;
        }
      }

      @media (max-width: 640px) {
        .ab-container {
          padding: 0 var(--ab-s-4);
        }

        .hero__title {
          font-size: clamp(42px, 14vw, 72px);
        }

        .hero__copy {
          font-size: var(--ab-size-md);
        }

        .plugin-body,
        .plugin-card__frame,
        .footer-card,
        .plugin-modal-header,
        .hero-code-block,
        .hero-example-header {
          padding-left: var(--ab-s-4);
          padding-right: var(--ab-s-4);
        }

        .plugin-modal {
          width: calc(100vw - 20px);
          max-height: calc(100vh - 20px);
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <header class="ab-topbar">
      <a class="ab-topbar__brand" href="index.html">
        <svg class="ab-mark" viewBox="0 0 32 32" aria-hidden="true">
          <rect x="2" y="9" width="28" height="18" fill="var(--ab-accent)"></rect>
          <rect x="2" y="5" width="28" height="6" fill="var(--ab-ink)"></rect>
          <rect x="12" y="14" width="8" height="3" fill="var(--ab-vellum)" opacity=".9"></rect>
          <rect x="2" y="5" width="28" height="22" fill="none" stroke="var(--ab-ink)" stroke-width="1.2"></rect>
        </svg>
        <span>abx-plugins <small>Plugin Marketplace</small></span>
      </a>
      <nav class="ab-topbar__nav">
        <a href="#browser">Catalog</a>
        <a href="#context">Context</a>
        <a href="#resources">Resources</a>
      </nav>
      <a class="ab-btn ab-btn--primary ab-btn--sm" href="https://github.com/ArchiveBox/abx-plugins/pulls" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Submit plugin</a>
    </header>

    <main>
      <section class="hero">
        <div class="ab-container">
          <div class="hero__masthead">
            <div>
              <span class="ab-eyebrow">Save the content that matters most.</span>
              <h1 class="hero__title">ArchiveBox <em>Plugin</em> Gallery</h1>
              <p class="hero__copy">
                Browse the plugins that ArchiveBox &amp; abx-dl use to archive content from websites.
              </p>
              <div class="hero__actions">
                <a class="ab-btn ab-btn--primary ab-btn--lg" href="https://github.com/ArchiveBox/abx-plugins" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Browse source</a>
                <a class="ab-btn ab-btn--lg" href="#browser">Jump to plugins</a>
              </div>
              <div class="hero__support">
                <code>ArchiveBox</code>
                <code>abx-dl</code>
                <code>abxpkg</code>
                <code>hook scripts</code>
                <code>config.json</code>
              </div>
              <div class="hero__stats">
                <div class="stat">
                  <span>Plugins</span>
                  <strong>{{ site.plugin_count }}</strong>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <section class="hero-example" aria-labelledby="quickstart-heading">
            <div class="hero-example-header">
              <div>
                <h2 class="hero-example-title" id="quickstart-heading">Run The Selected Plugin</h2>
                <p class="hero-example-copy">
                  Pick some plugins below and copy the command to run them.
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="hero-runner-links">
                <span>Get:</span>
                <a class="runner-link" href="https://github.com/ArchiveBox/abx-dl#readme" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">abx-dl</a>
                <a class="runner-link" href="https://github.com/ArchiveBox/ArchiveBox#readme" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">ArchiveBox</a>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="hero-code-block">
              <div class="hero-code-toolbar">
                <div class="hero-code-meta">
                  <span class="hero-code-kicker">Quick Start</span>
                  <code id="selected-plugin-name">abx-dl</code>
                </div>
                <button type="button" class="copy-button" id="copy-example-button">Copy</button>
              </div>
              <div class="ab-terminal">
                <div class="ab-terminal__bar">
                  <div class="ab-terminal__dots"><span class="ab-terminal__dot"></span><span class="ab-terminal__dot"></span><span class="ab-terminal__dot"></span></div>
                  <span>~/archive · abx-dl · quickstart</span>
                </div>
                <div class="ab-terminal__body">
                  <pre><code id="hero-command-example" aria-live="polite"></code></pre>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <details class="install-details">
              <summary>Expand to see pip install details</summary>
              <div class="ab-terminal">
                <div class="ab-terminal__bar">
                  <div class="ab-terminal__dots"><span class="ab-terminal__dot"></span><span class="ab-terminal__dot"></span><span class="ab-terminal__dot"></span></div>
                  <span>~/archive · setup · pip install details</span>
                </div>
                <div class="ab-terminal__body">
                  <pre><code data-highlight-shell>pip install abx-dl
abx-dl install
mkdir archive
cd archive
abx-dl 'https://example.com'</code></pre>
                </div>
              </div>
            </details>
          </section>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="catalog-toolbar" id="browser">
        <div class="ab-container">
          <div class="catalog-toolbar__grid">
            <label class="ab-field searchbox" for="plugin-search">
              <span class="ab-label">Filter The Catalog</span>
              <span class="searchbox__control">
                <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8">
                  <circle cx="11" cy="11" r="7"></circle>
                  <path d="M20 20l-3.5-3.5"></path>
                </svg>
                <input
                  class="ab-input"
                  id="plugin-search"
                  type="search"
                  placeholder="Filter by plugin name, hook, config key, or description"
                  autocomplete="off"
                  spellcheck="false"
                >
              </span>
            </label>
            <div class="result-count"><span id="visible-count">{{ site.plugin_count }}</span> / {{ site.plugin_count }} visible</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="catalog">
        <div class="ab-container">
          <div class="catalog__head">
            <div>
              <span class="ab-eyebrow">Catalog</span>
              <h2>Plugins, extractor hooks, and dependency records.</h2>
            </div>
            <span class="ab-meta">Open any entry for commands, hook scripts, config, and dependency details.</span>
          </div>

          <main class="gallery" id="plugin-gallery">
            {% for plugin in site.plugins %}
            <details
              id="{{ plugin.name }}"
              class="plugin-card{% if 'Snapshot' in plugin.phases %} plugin-card--snapshot{% elif plugin.phases == ['Crawl'] %} plugin-card--crawl-only{% elif plugin.phases == ['Binary'] %} plugin-card--binary-only{% endif %}"
              data-search="{{ plugin.search_text }}"
              data-hero-plugin="{{ plugin.name }}"
              data-hero-abx-command="{% if 'Snapshot' in plugin.phases %}uvx abx-dl --plugins {{ plugin.name }} 'https://example.com'{% else %}uvx {{ plugin.commands.abx_dl }}{% endif %}"
              data-hero-archivebox-command="{{ plugin.commands.archivebox }}"
            >
              <summary>
                <div class="plugin-card__frame">
                  <div class="plugin-main">
                    <div class="plugin-title-row">
                      <h2>{{ plugin.display_title }}</h2>
                    </div>
                    <div class="plugin-slug"><code>{{ plugin.name }}</code></div>
                    {% if plugin.description %}
                    <p class="plugin-summary-description">{{ plugin.description }}</p>
                    {% endif %}
                    <div class="plugin-subline">
                      {% if plugin.display_order is not none %}
                      <span class="plugin-order">#{{ "%02d"|format(plugin.display_order) }}</span>
                      {% endif %}
                      {% if plugin.primary_language == "python" %}
                      <span class="plugin-language plugin-language--python" title="Predominantly Python hooks" aria-label="Predominantly Python hooks">
                        <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" fill="none">
                          <path d="M12 3c-4.4 0-4.1 1.9-4.1 1.9v2h4.2v.6H6.2S3 7.1 3 12c0 4.9 2.8 4.7 2.8 4.7h1.7v-2.4s-.1-2.8 2.7-2.8h4.6s2.6 0 2.6-2.6V4.6S17.8 3 12 3Z" fill="currentColor" opacity="0.92"></path>
                          <path d="M12 21c4.4 0 4.1-1.9 4.1-1.9v-2h-4.2v-.6h5.9S21 16.9 21 12c0-4.9-2.8-4.7-2.8-4.7h-1.7v2.4s.1 2.8-2.7 2.8h-4.6S6.6 12.5 6.6 15v4.4S6.2 21 12 21Z" fill="currentColor" opacity="0.6"></path>
                          <circle cx="9.3" cy="5.6" r="1" fill="#fff"></circle>
                          <circle cx="14.7" cy="18.4" r="1" fill="#fff"></circle>
                        </svg>
                      </span>
                      {% elif plugin.primary_language == "javascript" %}
                      <span class="plugin-language plugin-language--javascript" title="Predominantly JavaScript hooks" aria-label="Predominantly JavaScript hooks">
                        <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false">
                          <rect x="4.5" y="4.5" width="15" height="15" rx="2.5" fill="currentColor" opacity="0.2"></rect>
                          <path d="M10.3 8.1v6.4c0 2-1 3.4-3.1 3.4-1.7 0-2.7-.9-3.2-2l1.7-1c.3.6.6 1.1 1.4 1.1.7 0 1.1-.3 1.1-1.5V8.1h2.1Zm7.1 1.7c-.4-.7-1-.9-1.7-.9-.7 0-1.4.3-1.4 1 0 .7.5 1 1.8 1.4 1.8.6 3 1.3 3 3.3 0 2.1-1.7 3.3-3.9 3.3-2 0-3.2-.8-4-2.1l1.7-1.2c.5.8 1.1 1.4 2.2 1.4.9 0 1.6-.4 1.6-1.1 0-.8-.6-1-2-1.5-1.7-.6-2.8-1.3-2.8-3.2 0-1.9 1.6-3.1 3.7-3.1 1.4 0 2.5.4 3.3 1.6l-1.5 1.1Z" fill="currentColor"></path>
                        </svg>
                      </span>
                      {% endif %}

                      {% for phase in plugin.phases %}
                      <span class="chip">{{ phase }}</span>
                      {% endfor %}
                      {% for label in plugin.template_labels %}
                      <span class="chip">{{ label }}</span>
                      {% endfor %}
                    </div>
                    {% if plugin.required_binaries or plugin.output_mimetypes %}
                    <div class="plugin-summary-facts">
                      {% if plugin.required_binaries %}
                      <div>
                        {% for item in plugin.required_binaries[:2] %}
                        <span class="chip chip--binary-summary">{{ item.display_name }}{% if item.min_version %}&gt;={{ item.min_version }}{% endif %} <small>({{ item.binproviders }})</small></span>
                        {% endfor %}
                        {% if plugin.required_binaries|length > 2 %}<span class="chip">+{{ plugin.required_binaries|length - 2 }} more</span>{% endif %}
                      </div>
                      {% endif %}
                      {% if plugin.output_mimetypes %}
                      <div>
                        {% for item in plugin.output_mimetypes[:4] %}
                        <span class="chip chip--mime chip--mime-{{ item.css_class }}">{{ item.emoji }} {{ item.label }}</span>
                        {% endfor %}
                        {% if plugin.output_mimetypes|length > 4 %}<span class="chip">+{{ plugin.output_mimetypes|length - 4 }} more</span>{% endif %}
                      </div>
                      {% endif %}
                    </div>
                    {% endif %}
                  </div>
                </div>
              </summary>

              <div class="plugin-body">
                {% if plugin.description %}
                <p class="plugin-modal-description">{{ plugin.description }}</p>
                {% endif %}

                <div class="actions">
                  <a class="ab-btn ab-btn--sm" href="{{ plugin.source_url }}" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Source on GitHub</a>
                </div>

                {% if plugin.required_plugins or plugin.required_binaries or plugin.output_mimetypes %}
                <h3 class="section-title">Dependencies &amp; Outputs</h3>
                <div class="plugin-info-grid">
                  {% if plugin.required_plugins %}
                  <article class="plugin-info-card">
                    <span>Required Plugins</span>
                    <div class="pill-list">
                      {% for item in plugin.required_plugins %}
                      <a href="#{{ item }}" class="chip chip--link">{{ item }}</a>
                      {% endfor %}
                    </div>
                  </article>
                  {% endif %}
                  {% if plugin.required_binaries %}
                  <article class="plugin-info-card">
                    <span>Required Binaries</span>
                    <div class="pill-list">
                      {% for item in plugin.required_binaries %}
                      <span class="chip chip--binary" title="{{ item.title }}">
                        <code>{{ item.display_name }}</code>
                        <small>providers={{ item.binproviders }}</small>
                        {% if item.min_version %}
                        <small>min_version={{ item.min_version }}</small>
                        {% endif %}
                      </span>
                      {% endfor %}
                    </div>
                  </article>
                  {% endif %}
                  {% if plugin.output_mimetypes %}
                  <article class="plugin-info-card">
                    <span>Output Mimetypes</span>
                    <div class="pill-list">
                      {% for item in plugin.output_mimetypes %}
                      <span class="chip chip--mime chip--mime-{{ item.css_class }}">{{ item.emoji }} {{ item.label }}</span>
                      {% endfor %}
                    </div>
                  </article>
                  {% endif %}
                </div>
                {% endif %}

                <h3 class="section-title">Run It</h3>
                <div class="run-tabs" data-run-tabs>
                  <div class="run-tabs-bar">
                    <button type="button" class="run-tab active" data-run-tab="abx-dl">Run with <code>abx-dl</code></button>
                    <button type="button" class="run-tab" data-run-tab="archivebox">Run with <code>archivebox</code></button>
                  </div>
                  <pre class="run-tab-panel active" data-run-panel="abx-dl"><code data-highlight-shell>{{ plugin.commands.abx_dl }}</code></pre>
                  <pre class="run-tab-panel" data-run-panel="archivebox"><code data-highlight-shell>{{ plugin.commands.archivebox }}</code></pre>
                </div>
                <p class="note">{{ plugin.commands.note }}</p>

                <h3 class="section-title">Hook Scripts</h3>
                {% if plugin.hooks %}
                <div class="hook-list">
                  {% for hook in plugin.hooks %}
                  <article class="hook-card">
                    <span class="hook-card-file"><a href="{{ hook.source_url }}" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">{{ hook.filename }}</a></span>
                    <div class="hook-card-chips">
                      {% if hook.language_code == "py" %}
                      <span class="plugin-language plugin-language--python" title="Python">
                        <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" fill="none">
                          <path d="M12 3c-4.4 0-4.1 1.9-4.1 1.9v2h4.2v.6H6.2S3 7.1 3 12c0 4.9 2.8 4.7 2.8 4.7h1.7v-2.4s-.1-2.8 2.7-2.8h4.6s2.6 0 2.6-2.6V4.6S17.8 3 12 3Z" fill="currentColor" opacity="0.92"></path>
                          <path d="M12 21c4.4 0 4.1-1.9 4.1-1.9v-2h-4.2v-.6h5.9S21 16.9 21 12c0-4.9-2.8-4.7-2.8-4.7h-1.7v2.4s.1 2.8-2.7 2.8h-4.6S6.6 12.5 6.6 15v4.4S6.2 21 12 21Z" fill="currentColor" opacity="0.6"></path>
                          <circle cx="9.3" cy="5.6" r="1" fill="#fff"></circle>
                          <circle cx="14.7" cy="18.4" r="1" fill="#fff"></circle>
                        </svg>
                      </span>
                      {% elif hook.language_code == "js" %}
                      <span class="plugin-language plugin-language--javascript" title="JavaScript">
                        <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false">
                          <rect x="4.5" y="4.5" width="15" height="15" rx="2.5" fill="currentColor" opacity="0.2"></rect>
                          <path d="M10.3 8.1v6.4c0 2-1 3.4-3.1 3.4-1.7 0-2.7-.9-3.2-2l1.7-1c.3.6.6 1.1 1.4 1.1.7 0 1.1-.3 1.1-1.5V8.1h2.1Zm7.1 1.7c-.4-.7-1-.9-1.7-.9-.7 0-1.4.3-1.4 1 0 .7.5 1 1.8 1.4 1.8.6 3 1.3 3 3.3 0 2.1-1.7 3.3-3.9 3.3-2 0-3.2-.8-4-2.1l1.7-1.2c.5.8 1.1 1.4 2.2 1.4.9 0 1.6-.4 1.6-1.1 0-.8-.6-1-2-1.5-1.7-.6-2.8-1.3-2.8-3.2 0-1.9 1.6-3.1 3.7-3.1 1.4 0 2.5.4 3.3 1.6l-1.5 1.1Z" fill="currentColor"></path>
                        </svg>
                      </span>
                      {% endif %}
                      {% if hook.order is not none %}
                      <span class="chip">order {{ "%02d"|format(hook.order) }}</span>
                      {% endif %}
                      {% if hook.is_background %}
                      <span class="chip {{ 'chip--bg-daemon' if hook.is_daemon else 'chip--bg-finite' }}">background ({{ "daemon" if hook.is_daemon else "finite" }})</span>
                      {% else %}
                      <span class="chip chip--fg">foreground</span>
                      {% endif %}
                      <span class="hook-card-phase">{{ hook.phase }}</span>
                    </div>
                  </article>
                  {% endfor %}
                </div>
                {% else %}
                <div class="empty-state">No hook scripts are defined in this plugin directory.</div>
                {% endif %}

                <h3 class="section-title">Env Var Config Options</h3>
                {% if plugin.has_config %}
                <div class="config-table-wrap">
                  <table class="ab-table config-table">
                    <colgroup>
                      <col class="col-key">
                      <col class="col-default">
                      <col class="col-type">
                      <col class="col-aliases">
                    </colgroup>
                    <thead>
                      <tr>
                        <th>Key</th>
                        <th>Default</th>
                        <th>Type</th>
                        <th>Aliases / Fallback</th>
                      </tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody>
                      {% for field in plugin.config_fields %}
                      <tr>
                        <td><code>{{ field.key }}</code>{% if field.description %}<span class="config-key-desc">{{ field.description }}</span>{% endif %}</td>
                        <td class="cfg-default">{% if field.default is not none %}{{ field.default }}{% else %}<span class="config-table-muted">—</span>{% endif %}</td>
                        <td>
                          <code>{{ field.type }}</code>
                          {% if field.minimum is not none %}<br><small>min {{ field.minimum }}</small>{% endif %}
                          {% if field.pattern %}<br><small>pattern <code>{{ field.pattern }}</code></small>{% endif %}
                          {% if field.enum %}<br><small>{{ field.enum|join(" | ") }}</small>{% endif %}
                        </td>
                        <td>
                          {% if field.aliases %}<small>{{ field.aliases|join(", ") }}</small>{% endif %}
                          {% if field.fallback %}{% if field.aliases %}<br>{% endif %}<small>fallback: <code>{{ field.fallback }}</code></small>{% endif %}
                          {% if not field.aliases and not field.fallback %}<span class="config-table-muted">—</span>{% endif %}
                        </td>
                      </tr>
                      {% endfor %}
                    </tbody>
                  </table>
                </div>
                {% else %}
                <div class="empty-state">This plugin does not define a <code>config.json</code> schema.</div>
                {% endif %}
              </div>
            </details>
            {% endfor %}
          </main>

          <div class="empty-state" id="empty-state" hidden>No plugins match the current filter.</div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <footer class="page-footer" id="resources">
        <div class="ab-container">
          <div class="footer-intro" id="context">
            <div>
              <span class="ab-eyebrow">Context</span>
              <h2>ArchiveBox ecosystem, plugins, and web archiving context</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="ab-stack">
              <p>
                The web rots fast. News stories get edited, videos disappear, social posts vanish, and cited links break within a few years. ArchiveBox is an open-source self-hosted web archiving platform built to help individuals and organizations keep durable local copies of the web in standard formats like HTML, JSON, TXT, PDF, PNG, SQLite, and WARC.
              </p>
              <p>
                This marketplace documents the shared <a href="https://github.com/ArchiveBox/abx-plugins" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">abx-plugins</a> catalog used by <a href="https://github.com/ArchiveBox/ArchiveBox" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">ArchiveBox</a> and <a href="https://github.com/ArchiveBox/abx-dl" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">abx-dl</a>. ArchiveBox manages full collections and long-term archives, <a href="https://github.com/ArchiveBox/abx-dl" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">abx-dl</a> runs plugin pipelines directly, <a href="https://github.com/ArchiveBox/abxpkg" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">abxpkg</a> installs supporting binaries, and <a href="https://github.com/ArchiveBox/abx-plugins" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">abx-plugins</a> defines the hook scripts and config schemas that actually crawl pages, install tools, and extract per-site outputs.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

